quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  47,12,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vachaendesa avo vanotenda (muhumwechete wavo) uye vachiita mabasa akanaka kuParadhiso rine nzizi dzinoerera pasi paro; uye apo avo vasingatendi vachinakirwa nekudya sokudya kunoita mombe; uye moto uchava nzvimbo yavo yokugara"
  47,13,"Uye maguta mangani akanga aiine simba kukunda guta rako (Makkah) rakakudzinga, avo atakaparadza. Uye pakanga pasina kana mubetseri kwavari"
  47,14,"Akafanana here uyo ari muchiedza kubva kuna Tenzi vake neavo zvitadzo zvavo zvinoitwa sezvakanaka kwavari, apo vachitevera zvido zvavo (zvakaipa)"
  47,15,"Muenzaniso weParadhiso iro rakavimbiswa vatsvene (ndewekuti) mariri mune nzizi dzemvura idzo maraviriro nemweya wacho haushanduki, uye nzizi dzemukaka usingashanduki, uye nzizi dzewaini inonaka kune avo vanoinwa, uye nzizi dzeuchi hwakachenurwa, uye imomo vachange vaine ndudzi dzose dzemichero, uye nekuregererwa naTenzi vavo. Vakafanana here neavo vachagara mumoto zvachose vachipiwa mvura inokwata ichipisa iyo ichadambura matumbu avo"
  47,16,"Uyezve mukati mavo mune vanokuteerera (Muhammad (SAW)) kusvikira vabva kwauri, vanoti kune avo vakagamuchira ruzivo: “Chii chaarikutaura zvino?” Vanhu vakadaro ndivo vakavharwa moyo yavo naAllah, uyezve vanotevera zvido zvavo (zvakaipa)"
  47,17,"Uye avo vakatungamirwa, vanovawedzera kutungamirwa kwavo uye vanovapa Taqwa (Kutya Allah vovaita vatsvene)"
  47,18,"Vakamirira here chimwe chinhu kunze kwenguva kuti iuye ivo vakavarairwa? Asi mviro mviro dzacho dzakatouya; zvino kana yave pavari, vachabetserekana sei nekurangarira kwavo"
  47,19,"Naizvozvo chiziva (Muhammad (SAW)) kuti, Laa ilaaha illallaah (Hakuna mumwe mwari akafanira kunamatwa kunze kwaAllah), uye kumbira ruregerero pazvitadzo zvako uye nezvevatendi varume nevakadzi. Uye Allah vanoziva kufamba kwenyu, uye nenzvimbo dzenyu dzekuzororera"